# Debug-only API secrets baked into the debug APK. Edit locally, never commit.
# A committed template lives next to it as secrets.json.example.
# Pattern covers secrets.json plus per-provider variants (secrets.openai.json,
# secrets.openrouterfree.json, etc.); the .example template is safe because it
# ends in .example, not .json.
app/src/debug/assets/secrets*.json
